762
01:09:22,000 --> 01:09:27,892
Means Raphael himself did it, or, I don’t know. How can I explain?

763
01:09:28,000 --> 01:09:31,892
This Paramchaitanya is doing all kinds of things,

764
01:09:32,000 --> 01:09:37,892
and it does all this just to convince you about Sahaja Yoga.

765
01:09:38,000 --> 01:09:39,892

