01:11:50,000 --> 01:12:01,892
the more you develop this non-reacting attitude through your proper Agnya.

794
01:12:02,000 --> 01:12:09,892
Not anger, not silence, but a very pleasant temperament.

795
01:12:10,000 --> 01:12:13,892
That means people think that I have told you not to speak. No, no, you must speak.

796
01:12:14,000 --> 01:12:17,892
You must talk to people, you must laugh, you must enjoy;

797
01:12:18,000 --> 01:12:23,892
but all this should be full of joyous feelings.

798
01:12:24,000 --> 01:12:33,892
That’s what they say that Christmas is for a very joyous atmosphere.

799
01:12:34,000 --> 01:12:37,892
So they can’t do that way so they drink. I mean, after all,

