01:15:23,000 --> 01:15:27,892
but if you have no self-respect, you don’t respect your Realization,

832
01:15:28,000 --> 01:15:34,892
you are not deeply involved as to your own ascent and the help to others,

833
01:15:35,000 --> 01:15:36,892
it will not work out.

834
01:15:37,000 --> 01:15:40,892
I’m here to tell you all these things which Christ could not tell.

835
01:15:41,000 --> 01:15:46,892
I had to fulfil what  He wanted to say.

836
01:15:47,000 --> 01:15:51,892
All those things I am saying to you. It has already worked,

837
01:15:52,000 --> 01:15:53,892
you all have got Realization,

838
01:15:54,000 --> 01:15:57,892
but develop respect for yourself as Sahaja yogis.

839
01:15:58,000 --> 01:16:01,892
Don’t have funny ideas about yourself.

840
01:16:02,000 --> 01:16:05,892
Just know you are a Sahaja yogi and a Sahaja yogini.

841
01:16:06,000 --> 01:16:14,892
That’s what is needed for a person if he is today celebrating the birth of Christ.

842
01:16:15,000 --> 01:16:24,892
He came on this Earth who was actually Christ, full of innocence,

843
01:16:25,000 --> 01:16:34,892
who was the One who came as the embodiment of Shri Ganesha.

844
01:16:35,000 --> 01:16:41,892
I have given the proof of it to you, how the carbon atom looks like,

845
01:16:42,000 --> 01:16:47,892
and by which I have proved that Christ is the Alpha and Omega,

846
01:16:48,000 --> 01:16:53,892
while He is made out of Omkara and Swastika.

847
01:16:54,000 --> 01:16:58,892
All this we have experimented. We have found it. It’s there.

848
01:16:59,000 --> 01:17:06,892
With all this, what is the greatest achievement is to respect your innocence.

849
01:17:07,000 --> 01:17:08,892
Respect your innocence.

850
01:17:09,000 --> 01:17:14,892
This is what is to be asked for today: be innocent,

851
01:17:15,000 --> 01:17:19,892
